{"TopicId":187351,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"So is KSP dying?","CreatedByName":"Xavven","CreatedById":100398,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T23:27:24Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Xavven","CreatedById":100398,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T23:27:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThese forums seem so deserted lately and the devs haven\u0027t released anything in like, weeks. WEEKS I tell you. With no new updates since forever and no other updates planned, I can\u0027t help but feel... like KSP is dying!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nObviously kidding. I just found out KSP 2 was announced and I am\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Ebeyond hyped\u003C/strong\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T23:37:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree.\u00A0 Not enough free stuff.\u00A0 Won\u0027t add guns.\u00A0 It doesn\u0027t even run on my potato anymore.\u00A0 Game is ded.\u00A0 Later dudes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T23:39:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP is consistently dying for years already. When it finally happens., could anyone please warn me about? I will probably be busy fixing some bug on TS and will miss the event!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbalmyButtpleez505","CreatedById":199544,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T00:10:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyeah man, if they aren\u0027t adding anime waifus, just consider it dead...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T01:50:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653776\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566257244\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022100398\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xavven\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Xavven said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t help but feel... like KSP is dying!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653776\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566257244\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022100398\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xavven\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Xavven said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just found out KSP 2 was announced\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe king is dead, long live the king!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"traisjames","CreatedById":193253,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T03:01:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan\u0027t be too dead...they released an update just weeks ago.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tux1","CreatedById":172521,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T03:04:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean, there have been multiple DLCs released for it, and nobody has complained about it, so it is dying in that regard.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwaster","CreatedById":71262,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T03:29:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP is dead.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLong live KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Merinsan","CreatedById":57629,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T03:39:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, it is finally dying....because KSP 2 is coming!!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"aagun123","CreatedById":153929,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T05:34:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\neverybody dies\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tux1","CreatedById":172521,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T06:04:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223654094\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566272370\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257629\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Merinsan\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Merinsan said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, it is finally dying....because KSP 2 is coming!!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen I have a child, I die because that child now exists.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fulgur","CreatedById":195204,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T06:19:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do not want this game to die. I am a\u003Cs\u003En old\u003C/s\u003E young fogey and I like this game. Bah, humbug.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cheif Operations Director","CreatedById":183218,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T07:17:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653776\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566257244\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022100398\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xavven\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Xavven said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThese forums seem so deserted lately and the devs haven\u0027t released anything in like, weeks. WEEKS I tell you. With no new updates since forever and no other updates planned, I can\u0027t help but feel... like KSP is dying!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nObviously kidding. I just found out KSP 2 was announced and I am\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Ebeyond hyped\u003C/strong\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt first I thought you were serious lol\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bootsam","CreatedById":198563,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T13:23:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCool, KSP2. Just when I thought KSP1 was tough enough, im so late to the party I shall have to learn new ways to fail miserably. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kernel Kraken","CreatedById":181383,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T13:57:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah. Microsoft buying it and adding a bunch of useless, overcomplicated mechanics no one asked for kinda ruined it for me.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwaster","CreatedById":71262,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-21T03:50:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223654175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566279270\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022153929\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022aagun123\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 hours ago, aagun123 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\neverybody dies\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEvery Kerbal dies. Not every Kerbal really lives.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JadeOfMaar","CreatedById":167617,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-21T03:58:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/100398-xavven/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022100398\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/100398-xavven/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Xavven\u003C/a\u003E Everyone who\u0027s been around here a long time should know that KSP is and has always been dying. It\u0027s been going on for 8 years now with \u0022outdated graphics\u0022 and most of its updates don\u0027t bring new content (parts, gameplay mechanics...) like you expect from other major games. Aside from DLC, most of the weight of KSP updates are performance buffs and bugfixes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s official that Squad is still going to go on for a while maintaining and updating this KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP 2 is also incredibly harder, more faithful to real physics so most of us casual players may not be able to jump on it and hence, will stay on KSP 1.x.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis thread is finished now. Have a nice day. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: lol that sarcasm/rhetoric at the end. You got me good. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-21T04:02:17Z\u0022 title=\u002208/21/2019 04:02  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 21, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by JadeOfMaar\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheJimPire","CreatedById":192502,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-21T06:01:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust like any long standing game, people will always say the game is dying. Just look at eve online, which has been \u0022dying\u0022 since 2002, yet the servers are still up\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-21T06:01:31Z\u0022 title=\u002208/21/2019 06:01  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 21, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by TheJimPire\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fulgur","CreatedById":195204,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-21T07:38:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI believe that if this game is dying, we shall perform CPR. And then it will no longer be dying.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf it continues to die, we shall take it to somewhere with a NHS.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf it continues to die, we must send Martystu Kerman to steal the apples (?) of immortality from the Lord Kraken at Bop.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fraktal","CreatedById":184990,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-21T11:26:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGames tend to start dying when a sequel is announced due to marketing\u0027s obsession with appeal to novelty.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHence why I\u0027m in a low-key state of dread about KSP 2\u0027s announcement. And that\u0027s not sarcasm.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-21T12:20:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223655623\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566386795\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184990\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fraktal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n53 minutes ago, Fraktal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGames tend to start dying when a sequel is announced due to marketing\u0027s obsession with appeal to novelty.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nToo soon to know. KSP2 is being developed by another company, so there will no overlap on marketing efforts - other than using TTI\u0027s infrastructure. I expect Squad to defend their castle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP1 will endure as long it\u0027s profitable and/or useful. And always there\u0027s the chance that something goes wrong on KSP2 , so from a business perspective is premature to start to phase out KSP1 now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot to mention keeping their feet on a niche they may not want to risk KSP2 yet, as Linux and MacOS. I\u0027m seeing a lot of new Unity games claiming they cannot, yet, guarantee decent support for these platforms. KSP1, right now, is already there (even that with some issues).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, yeah. It\u0027s too soon to know.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-21T12:21:42Z\u0022 title=\u002208/21/2019 12:21  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 21, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Lisias\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EKraken damned Autocorrectors\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-21T21:45:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223655623\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566386795\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184990\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fraktal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Fraktal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGames tend to start dying when a sequel is announced due to marketing\u0027s obsession with appeal to novelty.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, then TES is a dead undead.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xavven","CreatedById":100398,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T02:43:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223655333\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566359904\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167617\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JadeOfMaar\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 hours ago, JadeOfMaar said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEveryone who\u0027s been around here a long time should know that KSP is and has always been dying.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaha! Yeah, totally. I joined these forums in 2014 and have lived through, sheesh, I don\u0027t know HOW many \u0022KSP IS DYING!\u0022 doom and gloom threads, and some even started as tangents inside other threads. I can be a sarcastic SOB sometimes, and I just couldn\u0027t help myself when I saw KSP 2 announced.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-22T02:44:20Z\u0022 title=\u002208/22/2019 02:44  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 22, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Xavven\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpaceMouse","CreatedById":126931,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T03:20:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653781\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566257841\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klgraham1013\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/19/2019 at 7:37 PM, klgraham1013 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree.\u00A0 Not enough free stuff.\u00A0 Won\u0027t add guns.\u00A0 It doesn\u0027t even run on my potato anymore.\u00A0 Game is ded.\u00A0 Later dudes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want a game that only runs on a Potato.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA actual potato.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would probably run on GladOS. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curveball Anders","CreatedById":107529,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T07:23:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656354\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566444051\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022126931\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SpaceMouse\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, SpaceMouse said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want a game that only runs on a Potato.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA actual potato.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would probably run on GladOS. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr SpudOS...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}